Sepertinya gudang pendingin.

00:07:14.320 --> 00:07:17.400
Segalanya tampak buram bagiku.

00:07:26.640 --> 00:07:27.560
Aduh!

00:07:32.760 --> 00:07:33.640
Oh tidak.

00:07:33.760 --> 00:07:34.640
Arjun.

00:07:35.200 --> 00:07:36.160
Arjun.

